{"tid":687862,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［垃圾玩具］籃球 VS 乒乓球邊樣更 on9？","createTime":"2018-06-02T15:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T02:17:37.000Z","uid":46849,"like":12,"dislike":77,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"17c26b7fb9583d40451bd631b2580f301fba5485","tid":687862,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:33:35.000Z","msg":"個人黎講乒乓波更垃圾<br />\n<br />\n1. 兩個都係要開冷氣玩，但乒乓波係直頭出室外玩都玩唔撚到，大風少少就收皮，on 撚 9<br />\n<br />\n2. 籃球就美國佬同黑鬼玩晒，乒乓波就根本蝗道，得中國自己玩撚晒<br />\n<br />\n3. 香港黎講，籃波就中學雞玩具，乒乓波就小學雞玩具<br />\n<br />\n4. 同人講籃球校隊，至少聯想到係 MK / 高大之類，乒乓波校隊？毒撚死開d 啦<br />\n<br />\n5. 街場黎講，兩樣玩具d 網都係爛架喇，但籃波都可以打落去，乒乓波就 dur 網諗起都 on9<br />\n<br />\n所以千祈唔好同人講你好叻乒乓波<br />\n除非你係大陸仔<br />\n講完 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1218c737496730ea4c480154ca2ebf893c8bba0e","tid":687862,"uid":179481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:35:09.000Z","msg":"原來係玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ade50e627be90ec6ec972b485757c484b5fdad","tid":687862,"uid":46849,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1218c737496730ea4c480154ca2ebf893c8bba0e","tid":687862,"uid":179481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:35:09.000Z","msg":"原來係玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:36:31.000Z","msg":"同爆旋陀螺、四驅車、Pokemon Go 差唔多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edfb2db141f21bf6458270ef4b5361a4b52a484a","tid":687862,"uid":46849,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:40:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n邊個連登仔係乒乓波校隊出黎講兩句 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2cfce919dcd901df64abb1647543f000656fc98","tid":687862,"uid":55458,"like":25,"dislike":16,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:41:15.000Z","msg":"玩